{"tid":159692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好多外國巴絲用TOR+VPN玩野】警收炸彈恐嚇電郵 急調網絡罪案調查科跟進","createTime":"2017-03-17T07:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T07:39:40.000Z","uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b617c97f2bc63231cd4ea66a8a1ce03ee079a460","tid":159692,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"警方收到炸彈恐嚇，有網民自本周一起，連續4日向警方發出恐嚇電郵，昨日更指「可能星期六不知邊間警署會有炸彈」，警隊已通報全港軍裝巡邏小隊，提醒前線人員要加強留意，由於電郵來自美國及新加坡，警方已將案件交由網絡及科技罪案調查科跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n警方內部WhatsApp群組流傳，指「電台剛用電郵通知全世界話，有人在網上聲稱會係星期六於警署放炸彈，但冇明目標，已通知pscu(巡邏小隊)訓示人員，要多加留意可物品及可疑人。」東網正向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a971c0b2fe6a5671d6922297d72f6a392930daa","tid":159692,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2bc2dbdb904498c4bdc9dcbd6f753e5214af29","tid":159692,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}